Pantheon Integration

Pinecone

* Stores future holds not yet revealed.

Scarab

* Converts failed climbs into route improvements.

Flood Eater

* Prevents revealing too many holds at once.

Semantic LiDAR

* Identifies hidden handholds and structural routes.

Recall Navigation Doctrine

* Allows revisiting previous holds when needed.

Herding Dog

* Prevents carrying climbers to the top instead of teaching them to climb.

